*Planeti* se vrti oko sunca. (Planets revolve around the sun.)
Naučnici su otkrili da postoji milioni *planeta* u svemiru. (Scientists have discovered that there are millions of planets in the universe.)
Postoje velike razlike između *planeta* i asteroida. (There are great differences between planets and asteroids.)
Mnogi *planeti* se sastoje od gasa. (Many planets are composed of gas.)
Astronomi su otkrili da postoji život na nekim *planetima*. (Astronomers have discovered that there is life on some planets.)